{"tid":1662480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為不被珍惜所以墜落 因為墜落所以不再被珍惜","createTime":"2019-10-18T19:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T01:53:28.000Z","uid":312857,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"deaecd84c0966bbdcde86f4919fc4b55af884f99","tid":1662480,"uid":312857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"記得呢一句係之前喺高登故睇返嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家讀緊大學。中學嗰時真心以為會同個ex一生一世，一齊長大一齊變老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以比咗第一次佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後慢慢佢屌厭咗我之後，就冇乜再點扑，感情都變得越嚟越差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得喺分手前幾個月，因為佢對我真係太冷淡，keep住每日淨係覆兩三個wtsapp, 對我好淡好淡。我哋鬧過交，佢仲出手打我打到我瘀晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我真係太愛佢，已經比晒自己所有嘢佢，所以犯賤唔同佢分手，仲做好多野希望可以令佢重新鍾意返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後我發現佢鍾意咗另一個女仔，但我依然賴死唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後佢狠飛咗我。<br />\n<br />\n乜你唔係話攞咗我第一次，一定唔會唔愛我一定唔會唔要我㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔係話要同我一齊讀大學，一齊出嚟做嘢、娶我㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解到最後你要咁樣對我，仲要將我俾咗第一次你嘅事唱晒出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就開始覺得，既然一個我全心全意付出曬所有嘢比佢嘅人，都可以咁對我，咁以後仲有邊個會真心對我好真心錫我，我仲可以相信邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然之後我就 再做唔到好全心全意咁愛一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔敢再將所有雞蛋放晒同一個籃裡面，我好驚會好似之前咁，佢一唔要我我就失去左成個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我對之後嗰幾個男朋友都做唔到好似愛嗰個ex咁 咁愛佢地咁上心咁投入<br />\n<br />\n之後我覺得，反正第一次已經唔喺度，俾人屌一次定俾100個人屌100次都冇分別，所以就開始有sp, 玩ons，拍拖又認真唔到專一唔到。<br />\n<br />\n但其實我知咁樣係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到我第時真係遇到一個好嘅、適合我嘅人之後，我變到依加咁，又配唔配得起佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家嘅男朋友珍惜我，對我好，我又de唔deserve 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fc259f1fa65461add96e8734de42f6fe7895aa","tid":1662480,"uid":312857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:21:47.000Z","msg":"Sorry for too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c170f9a1155cea5d1e4fe7cb65bdf6116129948","tid":1662480,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fc259f1fa65461add96e8734de42f6fe7895aa","tid":1662480,"uid":312857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:21:47.000Z","msg":"Sorry for too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"c3737972da1ee8555cfed39618de605eb849163f","tid":1662480,"uid":312857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c170f9a1155cea5d1e4fe7cb65bdf6116129948","tid":1662480,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fc259f1fa65461add96e8734de42f6fe7895aa","tid":1662480,"uid":312857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:21:47.000Z","msg":"Sorry for too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"tldr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過打咗好耐，read 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daa6327db2c7edcc4582f91bd3e678351a95d45","tid":1662480,"uid":55810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"睇完個title淨係想問你係咪打錯字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm